main-rheiner.de/homepage/julius.makanec/karl/skarsaur12.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Rogue against other classes, PvP servers...</span><hr size=1> Ok, i given up me Rake on blue servers, and I play shaman, warrior, necro on Vallon Zek now. <br>
<br>
