<br>
Lets talk mid lvls like 25ish <p><BR> </FONT><P><font size=4 color="#000066"><u>Ulthien of the Shanks, VZ</u></font> <BR> <font size=3 color="#660000">Tribal Metilsmith Shaman</font><BR> <font size=2 color="#996633"><strong>(reincarnated agnostic rake)</strong></FONT><P><P><i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubomban.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bomban</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/18/01 9:36:04 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/bombanrz/photo.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogue against other classes, PvP servers...</span><hr size=1> A rogue at 25ish, shouldnt win a 1 one 1 duel against any class.  If they do win, then the person that lost needs to quit.  <br>
<br>
Wizards, have magic/fire/cold base spells.  I dont think an untwinked rogue at 25 can get good enough resists to make the wizard go oom.  Doesnt need root, uses lag/shadowstep.  <br>
<br>
Necro doesnt even need a pet, damage shield and lifetap and lifetap dot, rogue is toast.  <br>
<br>
Mage, with a pet, rogue doesnt stand a chance, without...going to need alot of FR/MR.  <br>
